data.description: Welcome to Wooded Bliss just a click off paved Capac Road!  This Charming 3 Bedroom Ranch Home is located on a 5 Acre corner parcel! Enjoy your own nature retreat!  Super clean, delightful One-Level living Cape Cod-style home boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, with over 2.5 acres of pristine woods - Perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and hunters!  Everything New!   Key Features: - 3 spacious bedrooms, each with its own unique character and ample natural light. - A well-appointed Bathroom with private access from a Bedroom—(features an enormous walk-in-closet) - Large living room opens to spacious, bright & airy eat-in kitchen with newer Stainless Appliances, Cabinets & plenty of counter space. - A+ Mechanicals! - 2023 fully encapsulated extra deep crawl with lifetime warranty on Waterproofing System w Sump pump & all newly installed Pex Plumbing plus a New Water Softener.  -Professionally installed limestone driveway rated for a 90,000 semi-trailer.   - Over 2.5 acres of your own wooded paradise, providing endless opportunities for hiking, hunting, and exploration. - Easy access from corner of Speaker & Capac, to I-69 & nearby amenities.  If you're an outdoor enthusiast or simply seeking a peaceful retreat away from the hustle and bustle, this property is a rare find. Imagine stepping out your door to hunt, hike, or simply savor the serenity of your private woods.  Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a slice of Michigan's natural beauty. Schedule a showing today and make this charmer with 5 acres of wooded wonder your new home sweet home!
